snippet.title: Flintlock: The Siege of Dawn | Release Date Announcement Trailer - Xbox Games Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Get ready to embark on an epic journey with Flintlock, an explosive indie Souls-lite from the creators of Ashen, launching July 18th.
Pre-order now and dive into the world of god-slaying action-RPG adventures: https://www.xbox.com/games/flintlock-the-siege-of-dawn
